thread.title: Robert Walters
thread.title_full: Omni Financial reviewed by Robert Walters

author: Robert Walters
title: Robert Walters
text: I am glad I found Omni. They helped me and they can help you too. Richard cared about making this happen for me. The IRS said I owned like 2 hundred thousand but during the recession i couldn't pay to have my taxes done. Omni got it dropped to 33 and would of been 17 if I had proof of my child support . I bet he feels good at the end of the day helping others, I know I would. Thank you all at Omni Financial.
